Interface Module

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Caretaker, ObservableModel
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EG, Keyboard, Mix, Oscilloscope, Out, Player, Recorder, Rep, Seq, VCA, VCFA, VCFB, VCOA, WhiteNoise
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractModule, JSynEG, JSynKeyboard, JSynMix, JSynOscilloscope, JSynOut, JSynPlayer, JSynRecorder, JSynRep, JSynSeq, JSynVCA, JSynVCFA, JSynVCFB, JSynVCOA, JSynWhiteNoise

    public interface Module
extends ObservableModel, Caretaker
    Defines the behavior of a Module.
    Invariant:
    getPosition() != null, getCircuit() != null, getEntities() != null, getInputLabel() != null, getOutputLabel() != null, getInputByLabel() != null, getOutputByLabel() != null, getAllConnectedInput() != null, getAllConnectedOutput() != null
